    "description": "使用新型精密瞄准镜和可定制标线系统，掌握远距离狩猎的绝佳命中率。利用先进的夜视功能在漆黑的夜晚追踪和狩猎猎物，并提供新款可定制标线系统及选项，让您拥有更多装备选择。<br><br>其中包括：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/de2b5435e4b62d73c777e039e9fd1966.avif?t=1731925544\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><strong>垂钓者4-8X100夜视步枪瞄准镜</strong><br>使用尖端的垂钓者夜视步枪瞄准镜，体验黑暗中无与伦比的清晰度，该瞄准镜采用100宽镜头和现代白磷技术设计。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/d8ceccf10196244ed719d8c43ae90ce3.avif?t=1731925544\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><strong>奥丁4-12X33步枪瞄准镜</strong><br>通用型奥丁步枪瞄准镜可减少更换光学瞄具的次数，该瞄准镜的放大倍率范围为4-12x，使您能够在近距离猎杀和远距离射击之间无缝切换。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/c3c818bc3bc106fc32753457adc180bc.avif?t=1731925544\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><strong>赫耳墨斯3-7X33手枪/霰弹枪瞄准镜</strong><br>通过赫耳墨斯3-7x瞄准镜重新定义手枪及霰弹枪性能。这款创新型瞄准镜不仅升级了常规的1-4x放大倍率，还可减轻你的背包重量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/bb842557982d09f228bdd950460fc48f.poster.avif?t=1731925544\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/bb842557982d09f228bdd950460fc48f.webm?t=1731925544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106720/extras/bb842557982d09f228bdd950460fc48f.mp4?t=1731925544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>可定制标线</strong><br>五种新款标线让您拥有更多装备选择： 双中心十字、密位十字线02、横切标线、目标光点和V形标线。每款自定义标线均可在游戏中的任意瞄准镜上使用，以适配您的游戏风格。",
